aa(lp57
VThis is the paradigm of the satellite industry.
p58
aVSatellites that are no longer working
p59
aVare often left to deorbit over many, many years,
p60
aVor only moved out of the way as a temporary solution.
p61
aVAnd there are no international laws in space
p62
aVto enforce us to clean up after ourselves.
