VNow, Mount Everest is actually an interesting comparison
p124
aVof a new approach to how we interact with our environments,
p125
aVas it's often given the dubious honor
p126
aVof being the world's highest garbage dump.
p127
aVDecades after the first conquest of the world's highest peak,
p128
aVtons of rubbish left behind by climbers
p129
aVhas started to raise concern,
